plot.content:
This piece is part of the Plotted Islands generative collection bringing to life imaginary maps through the power of code. This is a A3 plot (420mm x 297mm) made with fountain pen inks on watercolor paper.

It has been put on market on May 2023 on Foundation.

prev.content: This plot is one physical counterpart delivered to the digital owner of 'Plottable Golden Train #111'. Plottable Golden Train includes many variations (bridges, cactus, clouds, eagles, colors,...) entirely generated with code at mint (generative art).
